\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased significantly, indicating performance degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"P99 increased by 32.03%, substantial for response time.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max showed significant variance affecting global service performance.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median decrease by 21.52% and P99 increased by 59.64%.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请根据以上信息进行详细的后续故障处理和分析。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据获取的异常调用链数据，我已经进行了全面扫描，来分析异常调用的延迟瓶颈及错误传播路径。以下是我发现的异常调用链情况：\n\n### 异常分析\n\n1. **显著延迟调用链**\n\n   - **Cart Service 和 Redis 的交互**\n     - 调用链: `cartservice -> redis`\n     - 操作: `HMSET`\n     - 正常平均耗时: 1361ms，异常平均耗时: 9933ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 7.29\n   \n   - **Cart Service 和 Frontend 的交互**\n     - 调用链: `frontend -> cartservice`\n     - 操作: `AddItem`\n     - 正常平均耗时: 3694ms，异常平均耗时: 30400ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 8.22\n\n   - **Checkout Service 和 Shipping Service 的交互**\n     - 调用链: `checkoutservice -> shippingservice`\n     - 操作: `GetQuote`\n     - 正常平均耗时: 9347ms，异常平均耗时: 57113ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 6.11\n\n   - **Checkout Service 和 Shipping Service 的交互**\n     - 调用链: `checkoutservice -> shippingservice`\n     - 操作: `ShipOrder`\n     - 正常平均耗时: 12518ms，异常平均耗时: 68092ms\n     - 延迟倍数: 5.44\n\n2. **错误传播路径**\n\n   - `cartservice -> redis` 的交互中，Redis响应时间显著增加，这影响了 Cart Service 的操作并进一步传播到整个 Checkout 流程中。\n   - `checkoutservice -> shippingservice` 的交互中，Shipping Service 的响应时间显著增加，影响了订单结算过程。\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"frontend->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时段平均耗时: 1361ms，异常时段平均耗时: 9933ms，延迟倍数: 7.29\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常时段平均耗时: 3694ms，异常时段平均耗时: 30400ms，延迟倍数: 8.22\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\